metadata.name: The Warrior
metadata.description:
It's a girl and she can be anyone, a doctor, a nurse, an artist, an ordinary passerby. In the terrifying times, we are all equal, each of us needs to make decisions, to be a warrior, or to just stend by. 

It does not mean that we are impersonal, we are all beautiful. So I added bright colors and to emphasize this beauty. 

Creator: Katerina Marchenko
Medium: Tulle
Year of creation: 2022
